{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"621f2846bf","title":"关于按照系统实行革命大联合的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0ca83a33f4","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":17,"articleId":"621f2846bf"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6","name":"红旗一九六七年第十六期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"87dfa5c6ff","name":"中央文革"},{"id":"b7a1c99161","name":"国务院"},{"id":"ddddc27d93","name":"中央军委"},{"id":"f10c9d6647","name":"中共中央"}]},"publication_details":{"08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7a253bb293","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革","index":0,"publicationId":"08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6","articleId":"621f2846bf"},{"id":"a2a9eb2f3f","type":"paragraph","text":"关于按照系统实行革命大联合的通知各省、市、自治区革命委员会（筹备小组）、军管会，各大军区、省军区","index":1,"publicationId":"08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6","articleId":"621f2846bf"},{"id":"3dc2e933b9","type":"paragraph","text":"并转各群众组织","index":2,"publicationId":"08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6","articleId":"621f2846bf"},{"id":"b1bfca0a77","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）各工厂、各学校、各部门、各企业单位，都必须在革命的原则下，按照系统，接照行业，按照班级，实现革命的大联合，以利于促进革命三结合的建立，以利大批判和各单位斗批政的进行，以利于抓革命、促生产、促工作、促战备。","index":3,"publicationId":"08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6","articleId":"621f2846bf"},{"id":"96cdea8b85","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）所有革命群众组织都应该以毛泽东思想为基础，经过充分协商，按照不同的具体情况，遵照毛主魔上述的指示办理。一切跨行业的组织，都应该在自愿的原则下，接行业进行必要的调整。","index":4,"publicationId":"08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6","articleId":"621f2846bf"},{"id":"9c58580a69","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央、国务院中央军委、中央文革","index":5,"publicationId":"08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6","articleId":"621f2846bf"},{"id":"5aba4a077d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年千月十七日","index":6,"publicationId":"08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6","articleId":"621f2846bf"}],"page":{"id":"7b145fad82","publicationId":"08af3418-cd1a-4993-b391-9ace493b3eb6","articleId":"621f2846bf","start":7,"end":7}}}},"__N_SSG":true}